6&s={SIZE}\" />棄game 了，d 5星卷未用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成十萬石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚佢停止營運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好呀<br />\n<br />\n呢個營運真係算比較有良心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎緊有新花嫁女 抽埋先算啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/161018_a63941fbdfafeed963e6abbf500f949b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F161018_a63941fbdfafeed963e6abbf500f949b.jpg&h=9c3d0527&s={SIZE}\" />發覺好多人升爆左呢隻 <br />\n<br />\n突破十層+能力果加晒<br />\n<br />\n但明明唔係十分好用<br />\n<br />\n唔同真係因為貪佢水手服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講全能穩陣遠攻角一定簡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/161207_8c9d3a18d319ce95a997def70bbd7fec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F161207_8c9d3a18d319ce95a997def70bbd7fec.jpg&h=2297abaa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蕾咪 打塔一流 大技全體異常無效化異加回體<br />\n但係天生技有d弱 剩係-40%傷害 同+20傷害<br />\n<br />\n遠攻（藍色系）我會簡呢隻<br />\n天生技 傷害+35% 另外目標遠距離又加15%<br />\n最重要係技能可以前後左右迴轉，打敵人同時又可以迴避<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/171143_4068193a98c4b67560ed870b1977c199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F171143_4068193a98c4b67560ed870b1977c199.jpg&h=2425c2dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f756a04f828f9985a85695f4c948dcee960a4353","tid":497283,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite