<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/171143_4068193a98c4b67560ed870b1977c199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F171143_4068193a98c4b67560ed870b1977c199.jpg&h=2425c2dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻係咪都布花嫁版？<br />\n<br />\n花嫁版rush 加全體50% critical 都好勁"},{"pid":"da77e6b306867374b2f2301455f6db3d64549a2d","tid":497283,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"同埋幾個月前岩岩玩 乜都唔識又冇攻略<br />\n<br />\n升爆左呢隻法師<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg&h=6ad4812e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重炮係重炮 招45ap 冰技3倍攻完打人4x萬 仲勁過人地rush 2rush 3<br />\n<br />\n但諗返覺得應該其實升左其他先好D 有段時間拎住呢隻野好多關都唔受我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699751c3d1d336d80bc899f7c8dffa2f637b92e0","tid":497283,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"反而玩到而家都唔係好識Guard 點chok 出黎<br />\n<br />\n睇攻略話迴避個下岩岩好食中攻擊 但好少出到"},{"pid":"5565226cb4fcb5c0253d3fcb9f4e9e1f4cf18724","tid":497283,"uid":73751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋幾個月前岩岩玩 乜都唔識又冇攻略<br />\n<br />\n升爆左呢隻法師<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg&h=6ad4812e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重炮係重炮 招45ap 冰技3倍攻完打人4x萬 仲勁過人地rush 2rush 3<br />\n<br />\n但諗返覺得應該其實升左其他先好D 有段時間拎住呢隻野好多關都唔受我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻game 物攻優勢大好多，天生技多變化好多<br />\n<br />\n紅色（物攻）天生技<br />\n（atk 全體up,  目標近離遠近 atk全體又up)<br />\n<br />\n藍色（物攻） 天生技<br />\n（傷害 全體up, 目標近離遠近 傷害全體又up, combo 累積 全體傷害又up)<br />\n<br />\n黃色 （物攻）天生技<br />\n(全體血量up )<br />\n<br />\n紫色 （魔攻） 天生技<br />\n大多數自己INT UP ONLY <br />\n<br />\n紅、藍、黃既組合多數可以成團<br />\n紫色真係有d格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果遲下出隻藍色同黃色係魔攻 成團就大好多"},{"pid":"883bc541c09d3fd385835396c2d33f95d02e50d6","tid":497283,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋幾個月前岩岩玩 乜都唔識又冇攻略<br />\n<br />\n升爆左呢隻法師<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg&h=6ad4812e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重炮係重炮 招45ap 冰技3倍攻完打人4x萬 仲勁過人地rush 2rush 3<br />\n<br />\n但諗返覺得應該其實升左其他先好D 有段時間拎住呢隻野好多關都唔受我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻game 物攻優勢大好多，天生技多變化好多<br />\n<br />\n紅色（物攻）天生技<br />\n（atk 全體up,  目標近離遠近 atk全體又up)<br />\n<br />\n藍色（物攻） 天生技<br />\n（傷害 全體up, 目標近離遠近 傷害全體又up, combo 累積 全體傷害又up)<br />\n<br />\n黃色 （物攻）天生技<br />\n(全體血量up )<br />\n<br />\n紫色 （魔攻） 天生技<br />\n大多數自己INT UP ONLY <br />\n<br />\n紅、藍、黃既組合多數可以成團<br />\n紫色真係有d格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果遲下出隻藍色同黃色係魔攻 成團就大好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紫色係自私角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個關格鬥場 打個隻金色野用紫色角就多 成隊紫色互加int 再轟， 一次rush total打300萬都得<br />\n<br />\n但其他關真係好少用 , rush 傷害又未必夠紅色高<br />\n<br />\n之前同FF 系列crossover 個隻黃色都可以打過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975c4660af1c1396ab1627b9de77d383c0ba02d5","tid":497283,"uid":73751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋幾個月前岩岩玩 乜都唔識又冇攻略<br />\n<br />\n升爆左呢隻法師<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F173247_fd0934d6f28b5e936170e8466bde52c4.jpg&h=6ad4812e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重炮係重炮 招45ap 冰技3倍攻完打人4x萬 仲勁過人地rush 2rush 3<br />\n<br />\n但諗返覺得應該其實升左其他先好D 有段時間拎住呢隻野好多關都唔受我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我玩左10個月到<br />\n一開波 蕾咪起手 升滿lv 就入人場打 <br />\n果時 冇咩人突10 我自己就存突石同石<br />\n直至出左女武神 就升爆左同突10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/183445_5edf9fd31ea16a7d80dce160a2e56f8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F183445_5edf9fd31ea16a7d80dce160a2e56f8d.jpg&h=91a7c518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻女武神用到花嫁系列出，就擺埋左一邊重"},{"pid":"84586faa7944b6dee1e80481312eb352a37a91ff","tid":497283,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"魔攻角有隻魔攻蕾米<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/183230_c3cae530b858668e0d57c78333037a06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F183230_c3cae530b858668e0d57c78333037a06.jpg&h=5c74fa9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/183232_b7e2a3b45363559cf2d869c6668cd22f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F183232_b7e2a3b45363559cf2d869c6668cd22f.jpg&h=56d76e78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/183235_cfa762ac182906e0913bfa2e39ac222c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F183235_cfa762ac182906e0913bfa2e39ac222c.jpg&h=a10b019e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加全體暴傷 被動全體每3秒回5%<br 